text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service

IRM 5.1.17, Third Party Contacts, is being obsolesced. All general third party contact (TPC) information has been transferred to IRM 25.27.1, Third Party Contact Program. Collection-specific TPC information, mainly related to the Integrated Collection System (ICS), is being simultaneously moved to IRM 5.1.1.10I, Miscellaneous Collection Procedures, Third Party Contacts.
IRM 5.1.17, dated 06-14-2011, is obsolesced. General TPC material has been transferred to IRM 25.27.1, and Collection-specific TPC information has been moved to IRM 5.1.1.10
